content: jteso: Merged a substantial PR #2645 adding email-plugin functionality with significant code changes (+122366/-12110 lines across 1412 files). Currently has an open PR #2642 for adding EmailClient for Eliza, related to issue #2641 which they created and has since been closed. Activity was concentrated on a single day this week, primarily focused on feature development work (67%) with changes distributed across code (47%) and configuration files (31%).
